These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, gardening, photography, skydiving
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, chef, firefighter, police-officer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, daisy, daffodil, begonia
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 3. the person who growsdaffodil is not to the right of the person who growsdaisy##8
 4. the person who growsdaisy is not to the left of the police-officer##8
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 7. the analyst is the person who growsbellflower##1
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is not the police-officer##6
 9. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
10. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the right of the firefighter##8
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##8
12. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who's hobby is photography and the chef##2
13. the person who growsdaffodil and the firefighter have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |     3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | photography | gardening      | skydiving | cooking |
| Job           | firefighter | police-officer | chef      | analyst |
| Music-Genre   | daffodil        | daisy            | begonia    | bellflower |

