.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, water
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, blood-red, blue, black
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, rowing, sailing
 1. the person drinking coffee and the person who likes blue have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who likes blood-red have different parity positions##9
 3. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 4. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the person who likes amber is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person who likes black##5
10. the person who likes amber is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who likes blue##2
11. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | water  | 7up        | coffee  | almond-milk |
| Hobby      | blood-red  | amber    | blue | black |
| Sport      | rowing | ice-hockey | sailing | lacrosse    |

