 7. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##8
 8. the person drinking milk and the person who's birthday is in june have the same parity positions##9
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
10. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
11. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
12. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##8

